  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to investigate, with a case-crossover design, the effects of a short course
      of preventive CPAP administered in the immediate postoperative period in patients at
      high-risk of developing postoperative pulmonary complications undergoing major vascular
      surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
